## Introducing Frames X: The Ultimate UI Kit & Design Handbook for Figma

Frames X emerges as a groundbreaking UI Kit and Design Handbook tailored for Figma users, designed to significantly expedite the design process. Envisioned as the most efficient toolkit available, Frames X enables designers to construct aesthetic and robust systems while aligning with best design practices. This comprehensive toolkit, maintained since 2017 and highly rated by over 2,500 individuals, is trusted by top brands and designers globally.

